rom lime) complement seafood excellently."}'::jsonb, '{}', '{"Mexican","Tex-Mex","Caribbean","Seafood"}', NULL, '{"summer","all_year"}', '{"beach","bbq","casual","party","poolside"}', false, false, false, true, '{"bottle","can"}', '{"330","355","710"}', '{}', 'year_round', 'mid', 92, 'https://www.corona.com', 'Official Corona website and brand history', 1)
